                Mr. Bowen  (Cardigan)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-671d182c-dfac-49a1-8b6b-9060eda3a428" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-03-09/debates/0f6a8244-0a71-4757-9045-bf8dadb317a7/IronAndSteelIndustry#contribution-671d182c-dfac-49a1-8b6b-9060eda3a428">
