<p class="">Might it not be regarded as living in sin?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ff321876-8dc6-41ed-9307-ca8e4bf2ea30" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
