                Brigadier Peto  (Devon, North)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-423af7e7-536f-4104-9107-867a1d04724e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
