            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a188975f-0fb8-420d-ab61-e26039b76c80">
                Mrs. Braddock  (Liverpool, Exchange)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a188975f-0fb8-420d-ab61-e26039b76c80" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
